'''Sand-casting''' was a type of art which was very common on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], a stolen [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] sand casting that depicted a [[Tusken Raider/Legends|Tusken Raider]] in battle and was valued at 2,500 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] was taken to a hotel room in the [[Starlight Lounge]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Genarius]] by the minions of the [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] [[Slavery/Legends|slaver]] [[Gomalo]]. Members of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] upper class saw these sand castings as unique conversation pieces.<ref name="GG7">''[[Galaxy Guide 7: Mos Eisley]]''</ref>

